*************************************
* Installation instruction for jORS *
*************************************

Dependencies
------------

You need the YARP bindings for Java.

By default, the Makefile expect following paths:
$PREFIX/java/libjyarp/lib

You can override these defaults by setting the $JYARP_LIB variable
with your custom path.


Installation
------------

> make PREFIX=[your prefix] install

For the documentation:

> make PREFIX=[your prefix] install-doc
